heritage.stsci.edu/ The Hubble Heritage Project] and [http://archive.stsci.edu/hst/ Hubble archives] by STScI\n* [http://www.cosmos.esa.int/web/hst Hubble archives] by ESA\n* [http://www.cadc-ccda.hia-iha.nrc-cnrc.gc.ca/en/hst/ Hubble archives] by {{abbr|CADC|Canadian Astronomy Data Centre}}\n* [http://www.n2yo.com/?s=20580 Hubble current position] at N2YO.com\n* [https://uphere.space/satellites/20580 Real-time Hubble location and tracking] at uphere.space\n\n{{Hubble Space Telescope}}\n{{Space observatories}}\n{{Exoplanet search projects}}\n{{European Space Agency}}\n{{European manned spaceflight}}\n{{GSFC}}\n{{NASA navbox}}\n{{Orbital launches in 1990}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Hubble Space Telescope| ]]\n[[Category:Space observatories]]\n[[Category:Great Observatories program]]\n[[Category:Ultraviolet telescopes]]\n[[Category:European Space Agency satellites]]\n[[Category:NASA satellites]]\n[[Category:Artificial satellites orbiting Earth]]\n[[Category:Edwin Hubble]]\n[[Category:Lockheed Corporation]]\n[[Category:Space accidents and incidents]]\n[[Category:Space science experiments]]\n[[Category:Spacecraft launched by the Space Shuttle]]\n[[Category:Spacecraft launched in 1990]]\n[[Category:Space accidents and incidents in the United States]]\n[[Category:Articles containing video clips]]\n", "text_old": "{{redirect|Hubble}}\n{{pp-move-indef}}\n{{short description|Space telescope}}\n{{Use mdy dates|date=February 2019}}\n{{Use American English|date=March 2018}}\n{{featured article}}\n{{Infobox spaceflight\n| auto = all\n| name = Hubble Space Telescope\n| image = HST-SM4.jpeg\n| image_caption = {{longitem|Seen in orbit from the departing {{OV|104}} in 2009, flying Servicing Mission 4 ([[STS-125]]), the fifth and final Hubble mission|style=padding: 2px 0;}}\n| image_alt = The Hubble Space Telescope in orbit\n| image_size = 300px\n| mission_type = Astronomy\n| operator = [[NASA]]{{\u00b7}}[[European Space Agency|ESA]]{{\u00b7}}[[Space Telescope Science In